### 4. Upload Product Image ONLY (Utility/Legacy)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/products/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="product-sample-1.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ../../test-images/product-sample-1.png
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 4. Update Product - PATCH (Admin Only)
@productId = {{createProduct.response.body.data._id}}
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/products/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "description": "Updated description: The ultimate gaming machine.",
    "stock": 50,
    "specifications": {
        "Storage": "2TB NVMe"
    }
}

### 5. Delete Product (Admin Only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/products/{{productId}}

### 6. Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/logout
